main event: Five military members reported a sighting of a bright white object, the size of a basketball, at Chanute AFB, Illinois.
interesting points: The object was visible for 2 to 3 minutes and had an irregular building silhouette.,Witnesses observed the object from different positions around the base.,The sighting occurred just after an intense snow flurry.,The reported time of the sighting was 0030Z on March 10, 1961.,Investigations revealed a satisfactory explanation for the observed phenomena.
